You are a dangerous man.

199
00:20:57,441 --> 00:20:58,430
你不同意？
Don't you agree?

200
00:20:58,642 --> 00:21:02,305
長官，我不是不尊敬你 不過你最好還是把我放了
No disrespect, sir, but you'd be better off letting me go.

201
00:21:09,052 --> 00:21:11,885
把我逼上絕路我就是個鬥士
A fighter is about the last thing that l am.

202
00:21:20,330 --> 00:21:22,924
難道你不認為這由我來決定嗎？
Don't you think l should be the judge of that, soldier?

203
